cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use AlterLab Academic Skills in your research or teaching, please cite it as below."
title: "AlterLab Academic Skills"
abstract: >-
  A suite of 209 Agent Skills across 16 research domains that turn an AI agent into a
  domain-specific academic research assistant, with executable evals, citation and integrity
  audits, and bilingual (English/Turkish) documentation. A content fork of K-Dense-AI's
  scientific-agent-skills, re-aimed at the academic faculty and research-lifecycle audience.
